exclusiveGateway.name: What rating did the company get?

serviceTask.name: Receive a rating from the company

sequenceFlow.name: Rating better than C or no rating

textAnnotation.text: Assumption: Working permanently is still possible even with a rating less than C
Assumption: You have to accept a job if a company wants you
Hint: Being creative and avoid the inlcusive gateway

Hint: Process is modeled from the point of view of a job seeker.
"Rating is visible after 1 year" is not modelled, since it is not necessary for the process.
Receiving Tasks are seen as an external "automated" services
Event which takes place at the beginning of every quarter
